    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a number of transport mechanisms that are used to move Certificate Management over CMS (CMC) messages. The transport mechanisms described in this document are HTTP, file, mail, and TCP.</t>
      <t>This document obsoletes RFCs 5273 and 6402.</t>
